body_html:
Ah, some confusion. It was the "translate.py" file that had this date not the "seq2seq_model.py".

I did a git log -n 1 tutorials/rnn/translate/translate.py that indicated that the file "translate.py" file did not change from January 2017.

See https://github.com/tensorflow/models/commits/master/tutorials/rnn/translate/translate.py

In the debug.txt file attached in previous comment there is indeed the "legacy_seq2seq" directory that was I think, modified in commit #0d8916f4b84e8687eb46696883b50b84ac6aa420 from March 2017.

Does this make sense?

Sorry for the confusion.

Alex.
